    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute dream of a car and it's honestly in showroom condition! I\u2019ve been so meticulous with it\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s incredibly clean inside and out, basically looking like it just rolled off the lot. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a buyer who will appreciate how well it's been cared for. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see this beauty in person!",
      "price": 44500.0,
