    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been my baby\u2014always kept in a cozy garage and pampered like royalty. It\u2019s in such flawless shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor today. No scratches, no dents, and it drives like an absolute dream! I'm looking for a new owner who will appreciate just how perfect this ride is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
